    dc:description "FIGURES 2–7. Morphological features of Macromia siamensis sp. nov. holotype: (2) head, frontal view; (3) head, dorsal view; (4) synthorax, oblique frontal view; (5) synthorax, lateral view; (6) secondary genitalia, lateral view; (7) fore- and hindwing, lateral view." ;
